 The Art of Community - How to connect "[the desire to contribute]" to lead to results
 2011/5/26
 [Jono Bacon] (Author), [Yoshiki Shibukawa] (Author)
 [Amazon https://amzn.to/2viw2xS]

 Practical [organizational theory] in the context of an open source community, a situation where there is no enforcement through employment contracts.
 The book is written by the Ubuntu community manager himself, so there are many concrete episodes
 On the other hand, it is messy because it is not organized and linked to the context of existing organizational theory